<h2>Syllabus</h2>

This syllabus is tentative and subject to change. 

<ul>

<li>Fundamentals: Circuit and packet switching, network metrics,
layering</li>

<li>Application layer: name resolution, web, video streaming</li>

<li>Transport layer: (de)multiplexing, error detection, reliability,
ordering, flow control, congestion control</li>

<li>Network layer: addressing, router design, supporting protocols,
routing</li>

<li>(if time permits) Security: cryptography, signatures,
authentication, TLS</li>

